channel.title: Why Is My RSPS Not Running?
channel.description: Hello, im using a SSH Client with CentOS 5 32 bit. All the MYSQL stuff is disabled and no it leaves me with the problem that i still cannot host my server. Its guaranteed the server because i can host other RSPS. I also tried changing the run it still does not budge. Thanks.

item.title: Why Is My RSPS Not Running?
item.dc:creator: @MoHW MoHW
item.description:
@MoHW wrote:

Make supre you dont have any torrent clients open. If so exit them then run the server. The port torrent clients use usually interupts with the port of your server.
